  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mining game meets <strong>hack-and-slash</strong>.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mining for minerals without enemies or time limits. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forge drills with puzzle-like smithing system. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Equipment with special effects that create synergies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Additional stages for strong miners. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/e7ac5e4e989303ae439d219a208bd012.avif?t=1773803230\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig into the ground to collect ores and treasure chests.<br>Aim for the 999th floor!<br>When your bag is full, return to the surface. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/030b298ba57fe40485d24dfc672a075e.poster.avif?t=1773803230\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/030b298ba57fe40485d24dfc672a075e.webm?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/030b298ba57fe40485d24dfc672a075e.mp4?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/d09d6f1415be3164cd322b1d4e5089c0.avif?t=1773803230\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the collected minerals to create new drills.<br> You might create the ultimate drill if you fit the ores into the blueprint smartly. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/cbcf94ba86e6884f8548db131f6b7189.poster.avif?t=1773803230\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/cbcf94ba86e6884f8548db131f6b7189.webm?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/cbcf94ba86e6884f8548db131f6b7189.mp4?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/e593bc8cdd7cf0f6fefd00f499d84cb7.avif?t=1773803230\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your drill might gain special effects.<br>Combine them effectively to strengthen your power!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >* Focusing on <strong>movement speed</strong> for carrying resources quickly?   <br>* Enhancing <strong>explosions</strong> for massive destruction? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The choice is yours! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/ef3e8a8d71bb3bf45ee2a6b10c408379.poster.avif?t=1773803230\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/ef3e8a8d71bb3bf45ee2a6b10c408379.webm?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/ef3e8a8d71bb3bf45ee2a6b10c408379.mp4?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/db2314df82c27e97751b44d24da1b13f.avif?t=1773803230\" width=400 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging stages await after reaching 999th floor.<br> The treasures awaiting you are equally <strong>powerful</strong>! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/9dd2e999ef46dbc4edde5becf111509b.poster.avif?t=1773803230\" width=500 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/9dd2e999ef46dbc4edde5becf111509b.webm?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/9dd2e999ef46dbc4edde5becf111509b.mp4?t=1773803230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/32179c446956c3c3b7a4682c0c18830e.avif?t=1773803230\" width=280 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >20% chance of piercing attack </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/b51cfde7d98bbe21c2e6f00843c1c484.avif?t=1773803230\" width=280 height=72 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sight area +5 after brightening up blocks 200 times </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recommended for:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those who enjoy grinding game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those who want to collect many items.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those who enjoy creating builds in hack-and-slash games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Those who seek a relaxing game.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Video Policy</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game can be streamed or have videos posted without prior permission, whether you are an individual or a company.<br>There are no restrictions on monetization or which parts of the game you can showcase.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Demo Save Transfer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tap the \"<strong>Get Demo Data</strong>\" button at the top right of the title screen to continue from the demo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2916770/extras/c29e8a3e47fb12ce5dfd6b9272204818.avif?t=1773803230\" width=500 height=170 /></span></p>",
